issue.title: fuzz, wallet_bdb_parser: BDB builtin encryption is not supported
issue.body:
```bash
$ echo "" | base64 --decode > wallet_bdb_parser-59ff9efe156dbfea288b238d55315b4810adafee
$ FUZZ=wallet_bdb_parser src/test/fuzz/fuzz wallet_bdb_parser-59ff9efe156dbfea288b238d55315b4810adafee
terminate called after throwing an instance of 'std::runtime_error'
  what():  BDB builtin encryption is not supported
```
